{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"e2FJ7pgw5EQL0eELVXBaS","title":"Static Factor Models with Thresholding","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"type":"note","desc":"","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"SFM.threshold","id":"e2FJ7pgw5EQL0eELVXBaS","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.threshold","alias":"#threshold","position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":1,"column":11,"offset":10},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.threshold"}}],"anchors":{"implementation":{"type":"header","text":"Implementation","value":"implementation","line":15,"column":0}},"fname":"SFM.threshold","updated":1635422533164,"created":1635421959801,"parent":"0R61RLuT7e3hswR2v6o0w","children":[],"data":{},"contentHash":"c19c41c2e1324d8c61053d7e069f431b","custom":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"static-factor-models-with-thresholding\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#static-factor-models-with-thresholding\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Static Factor Models with Thresholding</h1>\n<p><a title=\"Private\" style=\"color: brown\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\">#threshold (Private)</a></p>\n<p>Follow up to Liu and Chen 2016</p>\n<p>Liu and Chen 2020 JoE</p>\n<p>Liu and Chen extend static factor models and allow the loading matrix (which they denote confusingly as <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">A</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span></span></span></span></span>) to be different according to a thresholding mechanism.</p>\n<h2 id=\"implementation\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#implementation\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Implementation</h2>\n<p>Liu and Chen did have R code, though this was awful to follow up and basically only worked for their simulation study.</p>\n<p>An attempt was made at simplifying this and making it work for normal data.</p>\n<p>Preliminary results showed that this algorithm had significant convergence issues, and I'm not sure why.</p>","noteIndex":{"id":"PhD","title":"PhD Homepage","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"type":"note","desc":"","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"PhD","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"roadmap","alias":"roadmap","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":451},"end":{"line":12,"column":12,"offset":462},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"roadmap"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"PhD","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"Meeting","alias":"Meeting","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1,"offset":464},"end":{"line":14,"column":12,"offset":475},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"Meeting"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"PhD","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"TODO","alias":"TODO","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1,"offset":477},"end":{"line":16,"column":9,"offset":485},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"TODO"}}],"anchors":{"quick-links":{"type":"header","text":"Quick Links","value":"quick-links","line":17,"column":0}},"fname":"root","updated":1637563604861,"created":1595961348801,"parent":null,"children":["t58wEmhAtf1GlHmO","Wnsnl9Ff8hLGapBoL37BK","CQTUwoXQNcd0Y7la7IaAn","9s2d4L1UHWFWCdtORYT2Q","AiXOWFsdvi3BPZxcUMjIi","MsmFdXyWfizd5g8GGcObD","MXHvc8bQbNRRVCB0UogRy","T4FN6sDHfA9wxiZ7Dg5WX","jtZSk246bVVDfJy6cdpS1","2qGHFR7CcKOE0Meu7UU6D","qGmGYptDKW2WLwlsu2xJw","GvwoAWaYZxq1czYi3t3k4","ZIDZSAYP9a9L7jYhVMgcz","WOnXV41UlGcOQzEoTZzJU","fhf7Gdr3mhOUG1mU5twC6","AOvKFmg0tBcGmUASXaALX","qDVp6IFHf6FiUdSgxwZMA","P1J9LjuS